#

Borscht with Sour Cream

75 min
$10
250 kcal
Difficulty: 25%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodHearty

Description

A hearty and vibrant beet soup, served hot with a dollop of creamy sour cream, perfect for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • beets: 4 medium
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • carrots: 2, diced
  • potato: 1 large, diced
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • sour cream: 1 cup
  • fresh dill: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
